{
  "texts": [
    "Ultimately, they chose the \"calm and mature man\" voice to match an intellectual figure, philosopher Jean-Paul Sartre; P14 chose the \"intellectual female\" voice to align with a persona of \"professional female therapist in her 30s\", aiming for a mature voice that conveyed life experience and guidance, avoiding lively or quirky tones.",
    "Likewise, P2 highlighted the importance that the persona's identity and voice should be consistent: \"I seek something that fits the persona.",
    "For example, if I want a lovely companion, I would choose a sweet voice rather than a deep, rugged one.",
    "\"For several participants, their avatar choice also aligned with the chatbot persona (P1, P4, P10, P17, P18, P19).",
    "For example, P4 chose (teacher) for the chatbot playing their academic advisor, noting that the avatar was visible throughout the conversation and thus served as a visual reminder connected to who the chatbot was."
  ]
}